  IF {&SELF-NAME}:LABEL = "&Close" THEN
  APPLY "CLOSE" TO THIS-PROCEDURE.
  ELSE
  DO WITH FRAME {&FRAME-NAME}:
    DISABLE {&LIST-1} WITH FRAME {&FRAME-NAME}.
    ASSIGN
      {&SELF-NAME}:LABEL = "&Close"
      Btn_Update:LABEL = "&Update".
    RUN enable_UI.
  END.
END.

